title: Clanker's Cavern
description: I hope you like swimming and cycles.

general.name: Tooth Cycles
general.description: To begin the level we are going to dive deep to collect a few notes and a jinjo free Clanker. Gloop, the bubble-producing fish at the bottom of the level, is on a global cycle the moment the level starts. Getting to him fast is necessary for the best positioning and air supply. Three methods around outlined below.

general.name: Honeycomb Backflip
general.description: In 100% it is fastest to do a backflip in mid air to grab Honeycomb 1 and land back where you started. This requires a specific combination of button presses and timing.

general.name: Saw Blade Wonderwingless
general.description: It's fast and simple to go through the saw blades without using wonderwing
